Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:34.02,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}On the nose
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:36.90,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}On your toes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:40.50,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}Coming out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:42.80,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}Passing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.39,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}By the hour
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:48.17,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}By the tower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:51.91,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}Missed a beat on sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:56.76,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}You came and went so fast
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:59.51,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}We all live in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:02.71,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}Everybody else is here with me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:04.97,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}But you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:19.90,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}In a perfect world we'd all be more like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:32.51,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}In a perfect world we'd all be more like you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.97,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}我將去往那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:34.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}踩準時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:36.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你的心準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:40.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}我將悄然出現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:42.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}時間匆匆流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:48.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}高塔擦身而過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:51.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}日落後的彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:56.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}來也匆匆去也匆匆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:59.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}我們都生活在過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:02.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明明大家都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:04.97,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}但你卻不在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:19.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}若能變成你那樣 就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:32.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}若能變成你那樣 世界就完美了
